name: JLife
description:
A simulation of "conway's game of life" in the webbrowser, with a bunch of featues.

I really like the custom type feature, which lets you define groups of states, which get saved to your input type selection.

I think i did a pretty good job, considering how limited my knowledge was at the time.(still is :P)

The styling on the other hand is pretty bad. (weird scrollbar sections ðŸ’€)
